Subject: [PATCH] drm/radeon: wait for moving fence after pinning
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 4b41726aae563273bb4b4a9462ba51ce4d372f78
